item.title: I dled a server source and cant run it...?
item.dc:creator: @NewbieNewty Newty
item.description:
@NewbieNewty wrote:

“@a” is trying to compile the server, then run it, which is why you are getting 2 errors.

The first error is that the compiler can’t find your Javac (used to compile)

The second error is that the “runner” can’t find the main class, the Server file, because you haven’t compiled yet.
